@node "Intro" "What is AmigaTEd ?"

INTRODUCTION:

AmigaTEd is an ASCII Text editor with buttons.
You can load, save, print, open a Shell, delete text or lines, etc...
All operations available in buttons.
I think AmigaTEd is a simple program but very useful.

AmigaTEd not allows you to edit binary files. The program only saves
files in ASCII format.
@endnode

